Day 1 - Instructions
-----------------------------------------------
Subject: node NodeJS_Basics_Training_Day_1_Instructions.js
-----------------------------------------------
Getting acquainted with the NodeJS ecosystem?

This time we have something to add to your submission instructions. Read them below:
You are required to setup babel to use ES6 standards
Add an ESLint linter, configured with Airbnb guidelines
Create a run script in package.json to run your code through npm start
Any future assignment should be properly modularized along with the implementation of SOLID principles
Install the husky module in development dependencies, and add the following to package.json
"husky": {
   "hooks": {
      "pre-commit": "eslint ."
   }
}

